    <abstract>
      <t>This memo defines a standardized framework for extensible SNMP agents.  It defines processing entities called master agents and subagents, a protocol (AgentX) used to communicate between them, and the elements of procedure by which the extensible agent processes SNMP protocol messages. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
